<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <title>Google Trends SVI Data Gathering</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='/css/style.css'>
    <script type='text/javascript' src='/js/client.js'></script>
</head>
<body>
    <p id='title'>Google Trends SVI Data Gathering</p>
    <p id='author'>Web application developed by <strong>Dayu Wang</strong> (<a class='url' href='mailto:dwang@stchas.edu'>dwang@stchas.edu</a>)</p>

    <!-- Basic rules -->
    <div style='margin: 22pt auto 0 auto;padding:0;'>
    <table>
        <caption>N/A</caption>
        <tbody>
        <tr class='header-row'><th scope='row'>N/A</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td class='boxed-text'>
                <p style='font-size:10pt;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;'>Basic Rules of Using the Web Application</p>
                <p style='margin:6pt 0 0 11pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-5.5pt;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:5.5pt;'>&bull;</span>This application uses the SerpApi (<a class='url' href='https://serpapi.com' target='_blank'>https://serpapi.com</a>).</p>
                <p style='margin:6pt 0 0 11pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-5.5pt;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:5.5pt;'>&bull;</span>The user is required to provide a valid API key for the searches.</p>
                <p style='margin:6pt 0 0 11pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-5.5pt;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:5.5pt;'>&bull;</span>The user is responsible for all the cost generated by the searches.</p>
                <p style='margin:6pt 0 0 11pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-5.5pt;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:5.5pt;'>&bull;</span>The developer is <strong>not</strong> responsible for the success of any search.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Current project information -->
    <div style='margin: 26pt auto 0 auto;padding:0;'>
    <table>
        <caption>N/A</caption>
        <tbody>
        <tr class='header-row'><th scope='row'>N/A</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td class='boxed-text' style='text-align:center;border-color:blue;color:whitesmoke;font-weight:bold;background-color:blue;'>
                Current Project
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class='boxed-text' style='border-color:blue;color:blue;'>
                <p style='margin:0 0 0 11pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-5.5pt;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:5.5pt;'>&bull;</span>Project Title: Why Do CEOs Lay Low?</p>
                <p style='margin:6pt 0 0 11pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-5.5pt;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:5.5pt;'>&bull;</span>Authors: <strong>Yao Ma</strong> (<a class='url' href='mailto:yma27@huskers.unl.edu'>yma27@huskers.unl.edu</a>), <strong>Dayu Wang</strong> (<a class='url' href='mailto:dwang@stchas.ed'>dwang@stchas.edu</a>)</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Module 1 - Get SVI Data -->
    <div style='margin:40pt auto 0 auto;padding:0;'>
    <table style='margin-bottom:20pt;white-space:nowrap;'>
        <caption>N/A</caption>
        <tbody>
        <tr class='header-row'><th scope='row'>N/A</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td style='border:none;border-bottom:3px solid black;padding:0 0 1pt 0;font-size:11pt;'>
                <strong>Get SVI Data</strong>
            </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <form action='/' method='post'>
        <div style='display:block;margin:0;padding:0;'>
        <label id='api-key-label' for='api-key'>SerpApi Key:</label>
        <input id='api-key' name='apiKey' placeholder='Please copy & paste your API key here.' type='text' style='width:694px;' value='<%= getSviData['api-key'] %>'>
        </div>
        <p class='error' id='api-key-error'><%= errorMessages['api-key'][0] ? errorMessages['api-key'][1] : '' %></p>
        <div style='display:block;margin:16pt 0 0 0;padding:0;'>
        <label id='database-file-label' for='database-file'>Database File:</label>
        <input id='database-file' name='databaseFile' placeholder='Please select your database file.' type='file'>
        </div>
        <p class='error' id='database-file-error'><%= errorMessages['database-file'][0] ? errorMessages['database-file'][1] : '' %></p>
        <div id='csv-requirements' style='margin:0;padding:0;'>
        <p style='margin:3pt 0 0 16.2pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-8.1pt;color:#2c634c;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:8.1pt;'>1)</span>Only .csv files are supported.</p>
        <p style='margin:3pt 0 0 16.2pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-8.1pt;color:#2c634c;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:8.1pt;'>2)</span>In the input .csv file, the first row must be the header row.</p>
        </div>
        <div style='display:block;margin:16pt 0 0 0;padding:0;'>
            <label id='column-label' for='column'>Column to Search:</label>
            <input id='column' name='column' placeholder='Please enter the column to search here.' type='text' style='width:652px;' value='<%= getSviData['column'] %>'>
        </div>
        <p class='error' id='column-error'><%= errorMessages['column'][0] ? errorMessages['column'][1] : '' %></p>
        <div id='column-requirements' style='margin:0;padding:0;'>
            <p style='margin:3pt 0 0 16.2pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-8.1pt;color:#2c634c;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:8.1pt;'>1)</span>You can only search one column.</p>
            <p style='margin:3pt 0 0 16.2pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-8.1pt;color:#2c634c;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:8.1pt;'>2)</span>The column name is case-insensitive.</p>
            <p style='margin:3pt 0 0 16.2pt;padding:0;font-size:10pt;text-indent:-8.1pt;color:#2c634c;'><span style='display:inline-block;width:8.1pt;'>3)</span>The column must be present in the input database file.</p>
        </div>
        <p style='margin:24pt 0 0 0;padding:0;text-align:center;'><button id='get-svi' type='submit'>Get SVI Monthly Data from 2004 to Present</button></p>
    </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>